rComments: Professeure passionée et passionante. Mon seul regret est que les DGD sont beaucoup plus compliqués que le cours et le TA est completement perdu. Une bonne note est facile à obtenir (A+ alors que je ne mérite pas cette note) à partir du moment ou vous écoutez en classe.

A great prof! Everything is very straightforward and there are no surprises on exams. She has super interesting lectures and talks about her own research. I had the option to pick between this class and physics II and I would recommend taking this class if you have the option!

Awesome class and a sweet prof! No super complex math and she lets you use a cheat sheet for the midterm and final. Goes over answers to the midterm, assignments and quizzes and clearly tells you what to expect on tests. Great class and great prof!

Going into a biophysics class I wasn't sure what to expect, but she made the class such an enjoyable experience. She teaches at a great pace and makes sure everyone in the class can follow what she is teaching. Great prof!!
